snippet.title: IBM Research
snippet.description: IBM researchers work on a range of applied and exploratory projects to help clients, governments and universities apply scientific breakthroughs to solve real-world business and societal challenges. Explore how our global community of forward thinkers is pushing the boundaries of science, technology and business to make the world work better.
